This paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of generative models and adversarial training, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper focuses on semantic image segmentation, which is a subfield of graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
